{"tid":2274072,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"19歲學生被控「反極權」遊行襲警 律政司撤銷起訴 訟費申請獲批","createTime":"2020-11-06T07:46:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T11:07:23.000Z","uid":240362,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"6264801dbb124a6db4cc2351d5da832ade627425","tid":2274072,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T07:46:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/11081\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F11081&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9sF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=bb6cc487\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/11081</a><br />\n<br />\n#東區裁判法院第一庭 <br />\n#錢禮主任裁判官<br />\n#0929銅鑼灣 #提堂 <br />\n<br />\n陳(19) <br />\n<br />\n控罪：襲擊在正當執行職務的警務人員<br />\n<br />\n案情：於2019年9月29日，在銅鑼灣東角道與駱克道交界襲擊警員13417。<br />\n<br />\n🍾️律政司考慮所有證供後，認為沒有合理定罪機會，故撤銷起訴🍾️<br />\n<br />\n✅辯方申請三萬元訟費，控方就著訟費的計算有爭議。辯方的訟費申請最終獲批。"},{"pid":"1ddd8e98fc181f1465564c52c743515d12a4b291","tid":2274072,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T07:47:50.000Z","msg":"濫補<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66495448cec3b5369a7d72ff107d54a57cdf6cf2","tid":2274072,"uid":127929,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T07:48:00.000Z","msg":"13417祝你死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a049312aabfd4267cceb9568157a273d42769109","tid":2274072,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T07:48:58.000Z","msg":"又一單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8b460bca38397bf43932882d32b8b7f9c8fae96","tid":2274072,"uid":54975,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T07:49:11.000Z","msg":"鳩拉完發覺想砌生豬肉都冇機<br />\n柒到"},{"pid":"7d63622f9ca7ce82ac693088b3b36aaad3ee733b","tid":2274072,"uid":279333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T07:49